		<h2>SPOJ Problem Set (classical)</h2>
				<h1>9063. Shuffling cards</h1>
		<h2>Problem code: SHUFFLEK</h2>
	</td>
	</tr>
</table>

<p align="justify">
<p>      </p>
<table style="width: 100%;" border="0">
<tbody>
<tr style="text-align: center;">
<td width="50%"><a href="/SPOJ/problems/SHUFFLEK/en/">English</a></td>
